reading an eternal injustice and tragic beyond compare in 
this human world 
the body lay on a table just to the left of the entrance huge 
chunks of ice were scattered around the body to slow decomposition 
ive come to grieve over the students who died said a 
middleaged worker as he emerged from the building 
after seeing the body a trembling 24yearold woman could only 
berate the government that ordered the murderous attack 
the chinese government is crazy theyve gone way too far 
she said 
