bailey too is proud of being part of pauls life i feel 
hes touched down in all of our lives in different kinds of ways 
theres no dark side to this story that i can perceive 
others do see a dark side however and because of the 
controversy surrounding the use of the doomed anencephalic infants 
as organ donors pauls transplant was the last 
some experts contend the babies should be used because they will 
die within days and many infant organs are needed critics say 
