the plan stresses cutting debt principal and interest payments 
over continued lending to heavily indebted countries 
i ask you to compare the risks of inaction with the benefits 
of concluding transactions that meet the tests of realism and 
reasonableness brady said 
if banks follow the brady plan bank claims will be somewhat 
