mondays supreme court ruling clears the way for a civil fraud 
trial of milken 
the 2nd circuit court refused to assign the case to a different 
judge but barred pollack from approving the settlement until the 
supreme court acted on milkens appeal 
once settlement of the secs civil suit against drexel is 
concluded drexel formally will plead guilty to the felonies and 
